# StudioMind Backend Environment Variables

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# LLM API Keys — Choose ONE provider
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# OpenAI (GPT-4o-mini recommended for cost/performance)
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-your-openai-key-here
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Anthropic Claude (Best for creative design advice)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-anthropic-key-here

# GLM AI / Zhipu (Chinese market alternative)
# GLM_API_KEY=your-glm-key-here
# GLM_MODEL=glm-4-flash
# GLM_EMBEDDING_MODEL=embedding-2

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Cognee Configuration (Optional overrides)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Cognee automatically uses your LLM key for embeddings
# No additional configuration needed for self-hosted mode

# For production deployments, you can configure:
# COGNEE_DB_PATH=/path/to/cognee/database
# COGNEE_LOG_LEVEL=INFO

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Server Configuration
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Backend server host (default: 0.0.0.0)
# HOST=0.0.0.0

# Backend server port (default: 8000)
# PORT=8000

# Frontend URL for CORS (default: http://localhost:5173)
# FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Setup Instructions
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# 1. Copy this file to .env:
#    cp .env.example .env

# 2. Add your API key (choose one provider):
#    - OpenAI: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#    - Anthropic: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
#    - GLM: https://open.bigmodel.cn

# 3. Start the backend:
#    python -m uvicorn main:app --reload

# 4. Cognee will auto-initialize on first run
